About Us
Fresh Seafood and Legendary Tropical Drinks
At the Lazy Turtle, we encourage all our guests to be lazy and extremely relaxed and let us do all the work for you, from our legendary tropical drinks to our freshest fish and our prime steaks to our unique appetizers and our great burgers and sandwiches & salad bar. We thrive every day to make your experience as tropical, relaxed and lazy all while being nestled beneath the tropical coconut trees on the fabulous Indian river in Palm Bay & intercoastal waterway, surrounded by island music, enjoying your favorite food and beverages.
Always stay lazy.
